	<!--Change log for new version. Single line or multi line. Supports minimal markdown subset-->
	<ChangeLog>
		V 1.0.1
		- Fixed Menu too long on some resolutions. Menu is now slighly more compact and can scroll
		- Fixed "Debug UI Alert" was underneath the debug panel and could not be clicked.
		- Fixed UI Binding output too wide in some cases.
	</ChangeLog>
